Maven 2 Surefire Report Plugin

 This plugin generates a nicely formatted html report about the test result.  
 
 This plugin parses the all TEST*.xml generated in folder ${basedir}/target/surefire-reports and then render them into HTML through DOXIA.
 

*How to Use
 
-------------------
<project>
   ...
      <build>
         ...
         <plugins>
            <plugin>
               <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
               <artifactId>maven-surefire-report-plugin</artifactId>
            </plugin>
         </plugins>
         ...
      </build>
   ...
</project>
-------------------
